data.description: The Elston floorplan features a large kitchen and great room divided by a kitchen island. On the second floor, you are greeted by a versatile loft space and the laundry room. The owner's suite features a large bath and substantial walk-in closet. Cane Ridge is in a thriving location within the town of Summerville. This charming community offers homeowners waterfront views minutes from an impressive shopping center, and the brand new family YMCA.
